verbose_text: The expression level of Aggrecan gene was elevated by Sr and Si ions together within the concentration range of Sr ions 1-4 mg/L and Si ions 2-8 mg/L, as well as the expression of SOX9 gene was enhanced by Sr and Si ions at the concentration of Sr ions 4 mg/L and Si ions 8 mg/L.
evidence: enhanced by Sr and Si ions at the concentration of Sr ions 4 mg/L and Si
